Privacy Policy — Pomorix

Effective date: 01 March 2026

1. Introduction

Pomorix (“we”, “us”, or “our”) is committed to protecting your privacy and personal data. This Privacy Policy explains: (a) what personal data we collect when you use the Pomorix mobile application and related services (the “App”); (b) why we collect it; (c) how we use, store and share it; and (d) the rights available to you under applicable Indian law, including the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023 (“DPDP Act”) and related rules. By downloading, installing or using the App you accept the practices described in this Policy. If you do not agree, please do not use the App.

